---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import site from '../data/site.json';
---
<Base title="Affiliate Disclosure" description="How IgnitionSim is funded, and our commitment that affiliate relationships never change our verdicts.">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="crumbs"><a href="/">Home</a><span>/</span>Affiliate disclosure</div>
    <div class="prose" style="padding-top:24px">
      <h1>Affiliate disclosure</h1>
      <p>{site.disclosure}</p>
      <h2>What that means in plain English</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Our current product purchase links use the Amazon Associates program. If you buy through one, we may earn a commission.</li>
        <li>It costs you nothing extra — your price is identical whether you use our link or not.</li>
        <li>Commissions never influence our ratings, rankings or recommendations. We routinely tell readers to buy the cheaper option or skip a product entirely.</li>
        <li>Every Amazon button is required to open an exact product detail page. We do not use Amazon search-result links or silently substitute an accessory, bundle, or adjacent model.</li>
        <li>Manufacturer manuals, official specifications, independent reviews, and community discussions may be linked as clearly labeled research evidence. They are not shopping links and do not carry buy styling.</li>
        <li>If an exact Amazon listing cannot be verified, we omit the purchase button rather than send you to the wrong product.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>If any recommendation ever reads as bought-and-paid-for, that's a failure of our editorial standard — tell us and we'll fix it.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
